121
00:06:02,660 --> 00:06:03,700
Have a rest.

122
00:06:04,020 --> 00:06:04,900
Find a chance

123
00:06:04,980 --> 00:06:06,580
to ask other villages tomorrow.

124
00:06:07,100 --> 00:06:07,700
Yes.

125
00:06:15,930 --> 00:06:16,700
Are you here

126
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:18,630
