Lu Yan!

154
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:24,710
Come out!

155
00:07:25,060 --> 00:07:25,950
Lu Yan!

156
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:27,260
You brat.

157
00:07:27,330 --> 00:07:27,900
Father!

158
00:07:28,620 --> 00:07:29,370
