271
00:12:08,940 --> 00:12:09,820
Her name is Yu Dengdeng.

272
00:12:09,860 --> 00:12:11,410
She is the future Queen of our city.

273
00:12:12,180 --> 00:12:13,340
These are the one-month birth gifts

274
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:15,570
